{
  "text": "Let me take as an example one you said was called Himmler. He we are assuming from this that his higher self was of sixth density. And it was stated that Hamler had selected the negative path. But his higher self then dwell in a six-density negative type of situation? Could you expand on this concept? I am Ra. There are a no of beings which have attained the overfestation, which is the honor duty of the mind, body, spirit, complex, totality of late sixth density, as you would term it in your time measurements. These a negatively oriented mind, a body, a spirit complexes have a difficulty which, to our knowledge, has never been overcome for after a fifth density, graduation, wisdom is available, but must be matched with an equal amount of love. This love light is very, very difficult to achieve in unity when following the negative path and during the earlier part of the sixth density, the society complexes of the negative orientation will choose to release the potential and a leap into the sixth density positive, therefore the over soul which makes its understanding available to all who are ready for such aid is towards the positive. However, the free will of the individual is paramount and any guidance given by the Higher Self may be seen in either the positive or negative polarity depending upon the choice of a mind, body, spirit complex.",
  "timestamps": {
    "segment": [
      {
        "segment": "Let me take as an example one you said was called Himmler.",
        "start_offset": 20,
        "end_offset": 101,
        "start": 1.6,
        "end": 8.08
      },
      {
        "segment": "He we are assuming from this that his higher self was of sixth density.",
        "start_offset": 137,
        "end_offset": 218,
        "start": 10.96,
        "end": 17.44
      },
      {
        "segment": "And it was stated that Hamler had selected the negative path.",
        "start_offset": 234,
        "end_offset": 297,
        "start": 18.72,
        "end": 23.76
      },
      {
        "segment": "But his higher self then dwell in a six-density negative type of situation?",
        "start_offset": 306,
        "end_offset": 383,
        "start": 24.48,
        "end": 30.64
      },
      {
        "segment": "Could you expand on this concept?",
        "start_offset": 386,
        "end_offset": 415,
        "start": 30.88,
        "end": 33.2
      },
      {
        "segment": "I am Ra.",
        "start_offset": 458,
        "end_offset": 491,
        "start": 36.64,
        "end": 39.28
      },
      {
        "segment": "There are a no of beings which have attained the overfestation, which is the honor duty of the mind, body, spirit, complex, totality of late sixth density, as you would term it in your time measurements.",
        "start_offset": 526,
        "end_offset": 1188,
        "start": 42.08,
        "end": 95.04
      },
      {
        "segment": "These a negatively oriented mind, a body, a spirit complexes have a difficulty which, to our knowledge, has never been overcome for after a fifth density, graduation, wisdom is available, but must be matched with an equal amount of love.",
        "start_offset": 1211,
        "end_offset": 1969,
        "start": 96.88,
        "end": 157.52
      },
      {
        "segment": "This love light is very, very difficult to achieve in unity when following the negative path and during the earlier part of the sixth density, the society complexes of the negative orientation will choose to release the potential and a leap into the sixth density positive, therefore the over soul which makes its understanding available to all who are ready for such aid is towards the positive.",
        "start_offset": 1996,
        "end_offset": 3310,
        "start": 159.68,
        "end": 264.8
      },
      {
        "segment": "However, the free will of the individual is paramount and any guidance given by the Higher Self may be seen in either the positive or negative polarity depending upon the choice of a mind, body, spirit complex.",
        "start_offset": 3330,
        "end_offset": 4005,
        "start": 266.4,
        "end": 320.40000000000003
      }
